The makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar â€” and the visionary, National Awardâ€“winning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend â€“ Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend â€“ Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies, and a saga that will echo through generations.

snippet.title: I Went to FFMIC and Total Gaming Became CS Champion ğŸ†ğŸ”¥ Live Reaction ğŸ˜³
snippet.description:
Today, I witnessed one of the best comebacks in Free Fire history! After four years, the Free Fire India Max Cup returned, and Total Gaming pulled off an epic BOOYAH! In the finals against GodL, GodL had a 2-point lead in the best-of-five series. But Total Gaming made an incredible comeback, leveling the score 2-2. In the final match, with the score tied 5-5, Total Gaming clinched the victory in the last round. It was truly an epic comeback and one of the greatest moments in Free Fireâ€™s history!

A big shoutout and congratulations to Ajju Bhai, Total Gaming, Fauji ajay mafia and Delete & all for their outstanding performance! Also, kudos to Jonty Gaming and NG Pros for their amazing gameplay. And letâ€™s not forget Marco from the GodL team, whose sniping was absolutely top notch!

All the best to everyone in the battle royale matches today

te.title: Amma Bhavani Lokalanele Song | Dasara Special 2025 | Telugu Devotional Songs | Durga Devi Songs
te.description:
Celebrate this Dasara Festival 2025 with the Divine Amma Bhavani Lokalanele Song. This Beautiful Telugu Devotional Song is dedicated to Durga Devi and filled with Devotion, Energy, and Festive Vibes. Perfect for Navratri, Bathukamma, and Dussehra celebrations, This Song will fill your Heart with Spiritual Strength and Blessings.

Song info:

Song: Amma Bhavani
Singer: S. P. Balasubrahmanyam
Lyrics: Chirravuri Vijay Kumar
Music: S. A. Rajkumar
Album: Siva Rama Raju
